title: One Day Without Shoes 2016
description: Today is the annual day when we take off our shoes to raise global awareness for children’s health and education. Post a photo to Instagram of your bare feet or your TOMS Shoes with the hashtag #withoutshoes. Join us by going #withoutshoes to help children in need around the world!
